        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Keycloak — Auth & Identity\nHandles login, token issuance, Google identity-provider brokering, and admin-API user provisioning for the invite flow. **Look here when:** users can't sign in, invite acceptance doesn't create an account, or the API starts returning 401s (it validates JWTs against Keycloak's JWKS endpoint). Keycloak logs plain text, so there's no structured `level` label — the panels use text matching."
      }
